    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1、前言"><a href="#1、前言" class="headerlink" title="1、前言"></a>1、前言</h2><p>现在很多网站提供的个人博客充满了各种广告，写起来也不方便，比如代码无法高亮等，让人没有想写的欲望，找了个时间研究了下目前常用的独立博客的做法，比较深受大家喜爱的是通过hexo建立博客。<br>本小白初玩博客，手头vps主机也不想浪费，准备这么玩：</p><ul><li>第一步：单台win7上实用Hexo+Github静态网页托管   （今天先搞这种）  </li><li>第二步：多终端（家里、单位）win7上更新博</li><li>第三步：将Hexo博客架设到VPS上，同时支持多台电脑更新博文</li></ul><h2 id="2、单台win7上实现Hexo-Github静态网页托管"><a href="#2、单台win7上实现Hexo-Github静态网页托管" class="headerlink" title="2、单台win7上实现Hexo+Github静态网页托管"></a>2、单台win7上实现Hexo+Github静态网页托管</h2><p>hexo是用nodejs写的一个简洁、高效的博客框架，通过md可以快速生成静态网页，其主题有很多种可供选择。hexo是免费开源的：）。<br>hexo.io中文手册：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a></p><h3 id="2-1-准备环境"><a href="#2-1-准备环境" class="headerlink" title="2.1 准备环境"></a>2.1 准备环境</h3><h4 id="2-11-github上申请账号"><a href="#2-11-github上申请账号" class="headerlink" title="2.11 github上申请账号"></a>2.11 github上申请账号</h4><p>github可用于开源代码免费托管，提供个人、项目两种方式的仓库，免费300M空间，在线仓库通过git可实现团队操作。国内用户需科学上网来访问。<br>申请主页：<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/</a></p><h4 id="2-12-下载Git、Node-js"><a href="#2-12-下载Git、Node-js" class="headerlink" title="2.12 下载Git、Node.js"></a>2.12 下载Git、Node.js</h4><ol><li>Git下载：</li></ol><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/download/win</a>            //本人下载的是(32-bit Git for Windows Setup)</p><ol><li>Node.js下载：</li></ol><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a>                                   //本人下载的最新版node-v9.5.0-x86.msi</p><h4 id="2-13-安装Git、Node-js"><a href="#2-13-安装Git、Node-js" class="headerlink" title="2.13 安装Git、Node.js"></a>2.13 安装Git、Node.js</h4><ol><li>Git安装</li></ol><p>双击安装文件，默认next结束，右击桌面选择“Git Bash Here”，进入Git，输入<code>git --verison</code>验证是否成功安装</p><figure class="highlight d"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen<span class="keyword">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 ~/Desktop</span><br><span class="line">$ git --<span class="keyword">version</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="keyword">version</span> <span class="number">2.16</span>.1.windows.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>Node.js安装</li></ol><p>node.js可以通过nvm安装，对于windows用户来说，建议使用安装程序进行安装。双击node-v9.5.0-x86.msi保持默认一路next安装结束。打开<code>cmd</code>输入<code>node -v</code>验证是否成功安装。</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Microsoft Windows [版本 <span class="number">6.1</span>.<span class="number">7601</span>]</span><br><span class="line">版权所有 (c) <span class="number">2009</span> Microsoft Corporation。保留所有权利。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">C:\Users\chen&gt;<span class="keyword">node</span> <span class="title">-v</span></span><br><span class="line">v9.<span class="number">5.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-2-安装Hexo"><a href="#2-2-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.2 安装Hexo"></a>2.2 安装Hexo</h3><h4 id="2-2-1-Git账户设置"><a href="#2-2-1-Git账户设置" class="headerlink" title="2.2.1 Git账户设置"></a>2.2.1 Git账户设置</h4><p><code>git config --global user.name &quot;xxx&quot;及email &quot;xx@xx.com&quot;</code>用于设置每次提交的作者信息，包括姓名和邮箱，–global表示对所有项目都使用这个信息。<code>git config --list</code>可查看设置。</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen@chen-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"cheneytac"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chen@chen-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"cheneytac@gmail.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-2-2-安装hexo"><a href="#2-2-2-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.2.2 安装hexo"></a>2.2.2 安装hexo</h4><ol><li><p>切换npm源</p><p>默认是通过npm来安装hexo-cli，在使用npm时，官方的源下载npm包会比较慢，国内一般使用淘宝npm镜像源，切换npm源过程如下：</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g nrm                  <span class="comment">//安装nrm （NPM源管理工具）</span></span><br><span class="line">npm WARN deprecated coffee-script@<span class="number">1.7</span><span class="number">.1</span>: CoffeeScript on NPM has moved to <span class="string">"coffeescript"</span> (no hyphen)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">C:</span>\Users\chen\AppData\Roaming\npm\nrm -&gt; <span class="string">C:</span>\Users\chen\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\nrm\cli.js</span><br><span class="line">+ nrm@<span class="number">1.0</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">updated <span class="number">11</span> packages <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">47.777</span>s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ nrm ls</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* npm ---- <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//registry.npmjs.org/          //当前默认源</span></span><br><span class="line">  cnpm --- <span class="string">http:</span><span class="comment">//r.cnpmjs.org/</span></span><br><span class="line">  taobao - <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//registry.npm.taobao.org/</span></span><br><span class="line">  nj ----- <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//registry.nodejitsu.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">  rednpm - <span class="string">http:</span><span class="comment">//registry.mirror.cqupt.edu.cn/</span></span><br><span class="line">  npmMirror  <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//skimdb.npmjs.com/registry/</span></span><br><span class="line">  edunpm - <span class="string">http:</span><span class="comment">//registry.enpmjs.org/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ nrm test</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* npm ---- <span class="number">965</span>ms                                <span class="comment">//测速 </span></span><br><span class="line">  cnpm --- <span class="number">270</span>ms</span><br><span class="line">  taobao - <span class="number">192</span>ms</span><br><span class="line">  nj ----- Fetch Error</span><br><span class="line">  rednpm - Fetch Error</span><br><span class="line">  npmMirror  <span class="number">4115</span>ms</span><br><span class="line">  edunpm - Fetch Error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ nrm user taobao                               <span class="comment">//切换淘宝源</span></span><br><span class="line">     Registry has been set <span class="string">to:</span> <span class="string">http:</span><span class="comment">//registry.npm.taobao.org/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>安装hexo<br>通过 <code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code>进行安装</li></ol><figure class="highlight moonscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen@chen-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line"><span class="name">C</span>:\Users\chen\AppData\Roaming\npm\hexo -&gt; <span class="name">C</span>:\Users\chen\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\hexo-cli\bin\hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL <span class="name">DEPENDENCY</span>: fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span><span class="number">.3</span> (node_modules\hexo-cli\node_modules\fsevents):   //fsevets是mac osx系统的相关依赖，在win下使用了，会有警告，忽略即可</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL <span class="name">DEPENDENCY</span>: Unsupported platform <span class="keyword">for</span> fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span><span class="number">.3</span>: wanted &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"darwin"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"any"</span>&#125; (<span class="name">current</span>: &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"win32"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"ia32"</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ hexo-cli@<span class="number">1.0</span><span class="number">.4</span></span><br><span class="line">updated <span class="number">1</span> <span class="built_in">package</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">28.257</span>s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>hexo初始化<br>hexo初始化是释放hexo相关文件，本人博客路径是e:/blog，因此需切换至该目录，输入<code>hexo init</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ pwd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Cloning hexo-starter to <span class="string">E:</span>\blog</span><br><span class="line">Cloning into <span class="string">'E:\blog'</span>...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Counting <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">62</span>, done.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Total <span class="number">62</span> (delta <span class="number">0</span>), reused <span class="number">0</span> (delta <span class="number">0</span>), pack-reused <span class="number">62</span></span><br><span class="line">Unpacking <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">62</span>/<span class="number">62</span>), done.</span><br><span class="line">Submodule <span class="string">'themes/landscape'</span> (<span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//github.com/hexojs/hexo-theme-landscape.git) registered for path 'themes/landscape'</span></span><br><span class="line">Cloning into <span class="string">'E:/blog/themes/landscape'</span>...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Counting <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">794</span>, done.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Total <span class="number">794</span> (delta <span class="number">0</span>), reused <span class="number">0</span> (delta <span class="number">0</span>), pack-reused <span class="number">794</span></span><br><span class="line">Receiving <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">794</span><span class="regexp">/794), 2.53 MiB | 854.00 KiB/</span>s, done.</span><br><span class="line">Resolving <span class="string">deltas:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">415</span>/<span class="number">415</span>), done.</span><br><span class="line">Submodule path <span class="string">'themes/landscape'</span>: checked out <span class="string">'73a23c51f8487cfcd7c6deec96ccc7543960d350'</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Install dependencies</span><br><span class="line">▒▒Ϣ: ▒▒▒ṩ▒▒ģʽ▒޷▒▒ҵ▒▒ļ▒▒▒</span><br><span class="line">npm notice created a lockfile <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="keyword">package</span>-lock.json. You should commit <span class="keyword">this</span> file.</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL <span class="string">DEPENDENCY:</span> fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span><span class="number">.3</span> (node_modules\fsevents):</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL <span class="string">DEPENDENCY:</span> Unsupported platform <span class="keyword">for</span> fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span><span class="number">.3</span>: wanted &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"darwin"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"any"</span>&#125; (<span class="string">current:</span> &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"win32"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"ia32"</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">added <span class="number">336</span> packages <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">51.206</span>s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start blogging with Hexo!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>最后输入<code>npm install</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">npm</span> install</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span>.<span class="number">3</span> (node_modules<span class="string">\fsevents):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: Unsupported platform <span class="keyword">for</span> fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span>.<span class="number">3</span>: wanted &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"darwin"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"any"</span>&#125; (current: &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"win32"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"ia32"</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">up <span class="keyword">to</span> date <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">13.475s</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-3-本地web访问"><a href="#2-3-本地web访问" class="headerlink" title="2.3 本地web访问"></a>2.3 本地web访问</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="keyword">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo <span class="keyword">is</span> running <span class="keyword">at</span> <span class="keyword">http</span>://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/. Press Ctrl+C <span class="keyword">to</span> stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1.png" alt="1"></p><h3 id="2-4-更换主题"><a href="#2-4-更换主题" class="headerlink" title="2.4 更换主题"></a>2.4 更换主题</h3><ul><li>官网主题地址：<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/themes/index.html</a>                   //目前189个item</li><li>知乎主题话题：<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/24422335" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zhihu.com/question/24422335</a></li></ul><h3 id="2-4-1-克隆下载主题"><a href="#2-4-1-克隆下载主题" class="headerlink" title="2.4.1 克隆下载主题"></a>2.4.1 克隆下载主题</h3><p>NexT主题目前10994个star，3239个fork，比较流行，目前最新版本是v6.0.3。项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next</a><br>将NexT主题克隆到本地，打开E:\blog\themes，确人已成功下载了NexT。</p><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen<span class="meta">@chen</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ git clone <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span></span><br><span class="line">Cloning into <span class="string">'themes/next'</span>...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Counting <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">1835</span>, done.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Compressing <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">21</span>/<span class="number">21</span>), done.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> Total <span class="number">1835</span> (delta <span class="number">5</span>), reused <span class="number">11</span> (delta <span class="number">0</span>), pack-reused <span class="number">1813</span></span><br><span class="line">Receiving <span class="string">objects:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">1835</span><span class="regexp">/1835), 909.43 KiB | 701.00 KiB/</span>s, done.</span><br><span class="line">Resolving <span class="string">deltas:</span> <span class="number">100</span>% (<span class="number">1055</span>/<span class="number">1055</span>), done.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-4-2-修改配置文件"><a href="#2-4-2-修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="2.4.2 修改配置文件"></a>2.4.2 修改配置文件</h3><p>修改根目录_config.yml， 找到 theme 字段，并将其值更改为 next。</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: <span class="keyword">next</span>                 <span class="regexp">//</span>注意空格</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-4-3-本地预览新主题"><a href="#2-4-3-本地预览新主题" class="headerlink" title="2.4.3 本地预览新主题"></a>2.4.3 本地预览新主题</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chen@chen-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="keyword">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo <span class="keyword">is</span> running <span class="keyword">at</span> <span class="keyword">http</span>://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/. Press Ctrl+C <span class="keyword">to</span> stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/2.png" alt="2"></p><h3 id="2-5-发布到github"><a href="#2-5-发布到github" class="headerlink" title="2.5 发布到github"></a>2.5 发布到github</h3><p>大体流程是本地hexo将写好的博文（MD文件），通过<code>hexo g</code>来生成public，然后通过<code>hexo d</code>将public文件内容推送到github，其他人即可用github二级域名来访问生成的静态网页。</p><h3 id="2-5-1-github建立仓库"><a href="#2-5-1-github建立仓库" class="headerlink" title="2.5.1 github建立仓库"></a>2.5.1 github建立仓库</h3><ol><li>新建一个仓库</li></ol><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1518054663429.png" alt="3"></p><ol><li>注意个人仓库的名字必须是username/username.github.io，后续可通过<a href="https://username.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://username.github.io</a><br>来访问你的个人主页，我的就是<a href="https://cheneytac.github.io，这里已经创建了，点create" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://cheneytac.github.io，这里已经创建了，点create</a> repository确定。</li></ol><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1518054984194.png" alt="4"></p><h3 id="2-5-2-添加ssh访问权限"><a href="#2-5-2-添加ssh访问权限" class="headerlink" title="2.5.2 添加ssh访问权限"></a>2.5.2 添加ssh访问权限</h3><p>本地客户端须通过ssh方式与远端的github建立联系，远端github作为一个仓库来接受本地客户端内容的推送。因此，本地客户端要生成ssh公钥及私钥，再将公钥传到github上。</p><ol><li>用<code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;cheneytac@qq.com&quot;</code>生成本地公私钥</li></ol><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx<span class="meta">@zjhx-PC</span> MINGW32 ~/Desktop</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"cheneytac@qq.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/c/Users/zjhx/.ssh/id_rsa):</span><br><span class="line">Created directory '/c/Users/zjhx/.ssh'.                        //保存目录</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):                    //输入密码，后面要用到</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /c/Users/zjhx/.ssh/id_rsa.</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /c/Users/zjhx/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:r81oJReKRT4ctNfzYOu22gIwnC7jB3IOVlFFN5eeX+U cheneytac<span class="meta">@qq.com</span></span><br><span class="line">The key's randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">+---[RSA 2048]----+</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">     ..++ o ..   </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">    .   oo +.   .</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">     o =....=. ..</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">    . = =...o=  E</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">   . . =So ..... </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">  + = o +.o.  .  </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string"> . * +   =. o    </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">    o . .=.o .   </span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">     . .o +oo    </span>|</span><br><span class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>复制.ssh下的id_rsa.pub公钥复制到github</li></ol><figure class="highlight tap"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 ~/Desktop</span><br><span class="line">$ cd /c/Users/zjhx/.ssh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">$ ls -al</span><br><span class="line">total 21</span><br><span class="line">drwxr-xr-x<span class="number"> 1 </span>zjhx<span class="number"> 197121 </span>  <span class="number"> 0 </span>二月 <span class="number"> 8 </span>09:40 ./</span><br><span class="line">drwxr-xr-x<span class="number"> 1 </span>zjhx<span class="number"> 197121 </span>  <span class="number"> 0 </span>二月 <span class="number"> 8 </span>09:40 ../</span><br><span class="line">-rw-r--r--<span class="number"> 1 </span>zjhx<span class="number"> 197121 </span>1766 二月 <span class="number"> 8 </span>09:40 id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">-rw-r--r--<span class="number"> 1 </span>zjhx<span class="number"> 197121 </span><span class="number"> 398 </span>二月 <span class="number"> 8 </span>09:40 id_rsa.pub              </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">$ cat id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">ssh-rsa  cheneytac@qq.com                     //公钥</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1518055806000.png" alt="1518055806000"></p><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1518055849658.png" alt="1518055849658"></p><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/1518055918397.png" alt="1518055918397"></p><p>输入之前创建的密码后，即可添加成功。<br>测试ssh访问github<code>ssh -Tgit@github.com</code></p><figure class="highlight vbnet"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">The authenticity <span class="keyword">of</span> host <span class="comment">'github.com (192.30.255.113)' can't be established.</span></span><br><span class="line">RSA <span class="keyword">key</span> fingerprint <span class="keyword">is</span> SHA256:nThbg6kXUpJWGl7E1IGOCspRomTxdCARLviKw6E5SY8.</span><br><span class="line">Are you sure you want <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="keyword">continue</span> connecting (yes/no)? yes</span><br><span class="line">Warning: Permanently added <span class="comment">'github.com,192.30.255.113' (RSA) to the list of known hosts.</span></span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="keyword">key</span> <span class="comment">'/c/Users/zjhx/.ssh/id_rsa':</span></span><br><span class="line">Hi cheneytac! You<span class="comment">'ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-5-3-建立ssh访问通道"><a href="#2-5-3-建立ssh访问通道" class="headerlink" title="2.5.3 建立ssh访问通道"></a>2.5.3 建立ssh访问通道</h3><p>修改E:\blog\_config.yml文件，最底下修改如下：</p><figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">deploy</span>: </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">type</span>: git                                              </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">repository</span>: git<span class="variable">@github</span>.<span class="attribute">com</span>:cheneytac/cheneytac.git         <span class="comment">//ssh或http方式，此处用ssh方式</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">branch</span>: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-5-4-发布博文"><a href="#2-5-4-发布博文" class="headerlink" title="2.5.4 发布博文"></a>2.5.4 发布博文</h3><ol><li>新建博文</li></ol><figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">"hexo搭建个人博客"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到E:\blog\source_posts下找到”hexo搭建个人博客.md“，然后使用你喜欢的md软件进行书写。</p><ol><li>发布到github</li></ol><p>用<code>hexo g</code>生成public资源，然后<code>hexo d</code>同步到github空间上，此时用<a href="https://cheneytac.github.io进行访问。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://cheneytac.github.io进行访问。</a><br>此时，恭喜你可以成功建立hexo博客了。<br>第一次发布需要下载插件，以后就不需要了下载插件。<code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p><figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">npm</span> install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> WARN deprecated swig@<span class="number">1.4</span>.<span class="number">2</span>: This package <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">no</span> longer maintained</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span>.<span class="number">3</span> (node_modules<span class="string">\fsevents):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: Unsupported platform <span class="keyword">for</span> fsevents@<span class="number">1.1</span>.<span class="number">3</span>: wanted &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"darwin"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"any"</span>&#125; (current: &#123;<span class="string">"os"</span>:<span class="string">"win32"</span>,<span class="string">"arch"</span>:<span class="string">"ia32"</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ hexo-deployer-git@<span class="number">0.3</span>.<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">added <span class="number">31</span> packages <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">23.146s</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight crystal"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g                                       /<span class="regexp">/生成public</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">INFO  Start processing</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">INFO  Files loaded in 2.23 s</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">INFO  Generated: index.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">INFO  Generated: archives/index</span>.html</span><br><span class="line">(此处略过。。。)</span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="symbol">Generated:</span> js/src/schemes/pisces.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="symbol">Generated:</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">lib</span>/<span class="title">font</span>-<span class="title">awesome</span>/<span class="title">fonts</span>/<span class="title">fontawesome</span>-<span class="title">webfont</span>.<span class="title">eot</span></span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="symbol">Generated:</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">lib</span>/<span class="title">font</span>-<span class="title">awesome</span>/<span class="title">css</span>/<span class="title">font</span>-<span class="title">awesome</span>.<span class="title">css</span></span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="number">53</span> files generated in <span class="number">7</span> s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo d</code>发布到github仓库中去，需输入ssh密码：</p><p><img src="http://p3thby42d.bkt.clouddn.com/ssh.png" alt="ssh.png"></p><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx<span class="meta">@zjhx</span>-PC MINGW32 <span class="regexp">/e/</span>blog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br><span class="line">INFO  <span class="string">Deploying:</span> git</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Clearing .deploy_git folder...</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Copying files from <span class="keyword">public</span> folder...</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Copying files from extend dirs...</span><br><span class="line">（此处略过）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span> This repository moved. Please use the <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">location:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">remote:</span>   git<span class="meta">@github</span>.<span class="string">com:</span>cheneytac/cheneytac.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">Branch <span class="string">'master'</span> set up to track remote branch <span class="string">'master'</span> from <span class="string">'git@github.com:cheneytac/cheneytac.git'</span>.</span><br><span class="line">To github.<span class="string">com:</span>cheneytac/cheneytac.git</span><br><span class="line"> + dfa99f6..<span class="number">.3</span>cb31f1 HEAD -&gt; master (forced update)</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Deploy <span class="string">done:</span> git                                      <span class="comment">//表示ok</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、相关报错处理"><a href="#3、相关报错处理" class="headerlink" title="3、相关报错处理"></a>3、相关报错处理</h2><p>按照以上步骤step by setp来建立，正常不会报错，用hexo写博文正确姿态应是：建立md文件–&gt;书写修饰博文–&gt;查看本地预览–&gt;发布到github。在此过程中有可能会遇到以下问题：</p><ul><li>修改参数或博文后，本地<code>hexo s</code>即报错</li><li>无法同步情况</li></ul><p>第1种情况需注意的是关键字后都有个空格，举个票子：</p><figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">deploy</span>: </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="attribute">type</span>:git                                               <span class="comment">//type关键字前缺tab键，冒号后缺空格</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">repository</span>: git<span class="variable">@github</span>.<span class="attribute">com</span>:cheneytac/cheneytac.git</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">branch</span>: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第2种情况请按照本文从头到尾再检查一边，另外可以先用<code>hexo clean</code>清掉public文件，再用<code>hexo g</code>来重新生成，最后再<code>hexo d</code>部署。</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zjhx@zjhx-PC MINGW32 /e/blog</span><br><span class="line">$  hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="builtin-name">INFO</span>  Deleted database.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="builtin-name">INFO</span>  Deleted public folder.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
